  // result), then the code will get stuck in the movement loop and
  // won't trigger the melee swap above. Check for this condition and
  // break out if it happens. Also, detect and break out of general
  // pathfinding failures. If the target is out of range and pathfinding
  // fails, then the NPC might say `cantReachRanged` dialog.
